snippet.textDisplay:
Hi Emma! You encouraged us to do product reviews, so consider this a product review for your channel lol. I really really like your videos. I like how streamlined they are, I love how funny you are, I really really really appreciate the fact that you're so real with your skin stuff, I feel like you're the most relaxed person about acne, like it's a thing, it happens, and you're still a rad and very pretty gal so who cares. I love how simple your concepts are! this may sound backhanded, but it really isn't, the fact that your concepts are easy to grasp make your videos always feel like such a breath of fresh air, like a walk in the park that brightens your day. The simplicity also really helps your personality shine through, which is a plus too. I like your fashion content too, how you make the high end luxury world more tangible and less uptight and annoying. I love how you present your sponsored content, it's very honest and natural and (most importantly) completely disclosed, which some other people don't do (and that drives me up the wall!), and you never collaborate with messed-up scammy stuff, I really appreciate that. I like seeing your cats! they're so cute, i was really happy for you when you got them, I hope they make you happy! Lastly, thank you for making content. It's free, and you clearly put effort into it, and I wanted to let you know I appreciate it! (the recent INANE, ABSURD backlash you got for the "dying my hair for no reason" made me so fucking mad, jesus. you put this up FOR. FREE.)
Thats it! I don't really leave comments, but I've been a watcher for a long time and the consistency and the quality of your work drives me to want to tell you how much I enjoy it. Much love!
